{"tid":2326022,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"沙田富臨薈疑欠租4個月 遭業主入稟追討163萬兼收舖","createTime":"2020-12-15T04:22:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T10:09:12.000Z","uid":130626,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"bd1b66a193d75890114b8611c36d1369a8345f34","tid":2326022,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:22:31.000Z","msg":"去年修例風波中被市民形容為靠攏「福建幫」的富臨集團，遭網民發起罷食抵制。集團旗下品牌富臨薈於沙田偉華中心的店舖，去年在《禁蒙面法》實施後更遭「裝修」。該店昨遭業主入稟高等法院，追討拖欠四個月的租金兼要求收舖，涉及租金連雜費等逾163萬元。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201215/RKXZHLC2KVABXDOH6Y7WUR5BEM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201215%2FRKXZHLC2KVABXDOH6Y7WUR5BEM%2F&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGJUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=9130c143\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201215%2FRKXZHLC2KVABXDOH6Y7WUR5BEM%2F&h=3fbe344c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201215/RKXZHLC2KVABXDOH6Y7WUR5BEM/</a>"},{"pid":"0acb68b63ad7858c69a17aca24150c408d490e8b","tid":2326022,"uid":54337,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:27:37.000Z","msg":"沉迷的大多數呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ee913174993f51a33683ae1fd982514779f2a9c","tid":2326022,"uid":11291,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:28:31.000Z","msg":"說好的藍色經濟圈呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d0122677ac7352042b2e23f2adc4e3249e798a","tid":2326022,"uid":178102,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0acb68b63ad7858c69a17aca24150c408d490e8b","tid":2326022,"uid":54337,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:27:37.000Z","msg":"沉迷的大多數呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\